{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require Direct Debit Charity Collections to be Licensed as cash collections are",
        "additional_details": "Apply the same conditions, standards, and oversight currently required for cash charity collections that local councils already adhere to.\r\n \r\nDirect Debit charity collectors approach people in the same way as cash collectors but aren\u2019t required to be licensed. This can create inconsistency, reduce accountability, and leave the public unprotected. Licensing DD collections would improve fairness, transparency, and higher standards.",
        "background": "Introduce a licensing requirement for all Direct Debit charity collections, whether conducted as street collections or door-to-door.",
